<p>I used to work in mental health services so I know personal goals can look drastically different for everyone. Things like getting out of bed, going for a walk to relieve anxiety, and making plans with friends when you'd tempted to stay in (again) can be a big deal if you're having a tough time.</p>
<p>Accomplist is a place to give yourself some cred for those victories!</p>
